title: Top Places to visit in Kavali, Andhra Pradesh
content: Kavali is the second-largest city in the Nellore district of Andhra Pradesh of India. It is one of the major cities in Andhra Pradesh. It is also known as Kanakapatnam, because of the fact that it is home to a lot of wealthy individuals and due to the prophecy from Potuluri Veerabrahmendra Swami,
